        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-03-13T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-03-13T18:00:00-05:00" n="472" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d472">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.248/3–1347: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-03-13T19:00:00-04:00">March 13, 1947—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>188. Retiring Chief US Air Mission now submitting report to <gloss target="#t_CDC1">CDC</gloss> with copy for Embassy on types airplanes he
                    recommends for Chilean Air Force. I am forwarding copy this report to
                    Department. One point which IX feel calls for early action is following: Chief,
                    Air Mission believes <gloss target="#t_B251">B–25</gloss> bombers of which 12
                    now in Chile under interim program and have not yet been transferred to Chile
                    are not suitable for Chilean Air Force program. Furthermore he has gained
                    impression from conversation with Chilean Air Force officers that Chile would
                    prefer not to purchase these planes owing very great expense operation and other
                    important limitations. Should Chilean Air Force actually express wish not to
                    purchase these <gloss target="#t_B251">B–25</gloss>’s would appropriate American
                    officials be agreeable? What disposition would be made these aircraft?</p>
                <p>In view imbalance Chilean budget I of course feel any steps which forces might
                    wish to make toward economy operation Expelles are highly desirable. Please
                    telegraph urgently.</p>
                <p>Repeated Panama for <gloss target="#t_CDC1">CDC</gloss>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bowers</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
